{"tid":124070,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［箍牙］箍完隱適美既你有無走位？求醫生介紹","createTime":"2017-02-17T10:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T23:35:19.000Z","uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a09e17181fd5d75481b71d4f74e8d7d97009469","tid":124070,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"之前箍過傳統既但唔知係咪箍完先脫智慧齒既關係宜家走曬位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打去以前箍牙既診所就話個醫生唔再做箍牙，幫人箍牙箍到走曬位之後就話唔再做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到宜家要再箍過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次想整隱適美，但唔知箍完幾年後會唔會走位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚又走位，箍完走位都唔知箍黎做嘜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求巴絲分享下箍完效果，同埋有無好醫生介紹"},{"pid":"b78b3db4bfb874c6cdd04878848d38a3bd138dbd","tid":124070,"uid":70423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"係咪冇戴Retainer呀之前。"},{"pid":"cc3fd60a154726a30005dfc09ef1e01e3a9b31d6","tid":124070,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪冇戴Retainer呀之前。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀！帶左一段時間就脫左4隻智慧齒，因為d智慧齒打橫生，迫到d生好痛，脫左之後就慢慢走曬位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b004b4ee793279425db14ec52c86e75772277ec","tid":124070,"uid":27181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪冇戴Retainer呀之前。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀！帶左一段時間就脫左4隻智慧齒，因為d智慧齒打橫生，迫到d<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">牙</span></span>好痛，脫左之後就慢慢走曬位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2ddddcda1bd5e70686f8b2440c796b5fe00c9c87","tid":124070,"uid":10572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"好似之前牙醫診所姑娘話<br />\n有3成客都係番手箍<br />\n所以應該係好平常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84bf4a7525d598340352bc6ea7cbbbd883d3b9","tid":124070,"uid":8222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"除左智慧齒有冇繼續戴 retainer"},{"pid":"3a966ad80af3ac07d6001b3e12542f35778b6f09","tid":124070,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aac31986ac31b9c623c1c541c5bef9489dd03c0","tid":124070,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c18b08bc3090c92fc4bf590c9a55c84bae345f00","tid":124070,"uid":27181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左智慧齒有冇繼續戴 retainer</blockquote><br />\n好似無，個時話帶一年既，咁脫個時都一年之後。仲要一次過脫曬4隻，痛到就黎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f7f7f87d65b6b2736ffa51dfc52650534eab9d","tid":124070,"uid":130761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹你去尖沙咀林靜怡<br />\n我cool完好好～</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想箍隱適美，請問可唔可以做我嘅介紹人?<br />\n我嘅TG係Wing1234"},{"pid":"0f08a068d9134c038805b0d1638ea2b590d6a1f3","tid":124070,"uid":99384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T23:35:19.000Z","msg":"我係康齒堂cool 又唔貴 如有需要 可搵我做介紹人 你可以減3千 <a href=\"https://t.me/marcolo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmarcolo&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3fd002ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/marcolo</a>"}]}